<h1>Memoranda concerning Western Defense</h1>

<div class="docbody">
<div class="opener">
<table class="salutationBlock">
        <tr>
		<td class="salutationRight">[ca. 8 June 1780]</td>
	      </tr>
      </table>
</div>
<h2>I</h2>
<ul class="simple">
	    <li>Write to Colo. Bowman.</li>
	    <li style="margin-left: 2em;">order on Colo. Fleming to send 1000  powd[er.]</li>
	    <li style="margin-left: 2em;">do. Lynch 3000 lead.</li>
	    <li style="text-indent: -1.5em; padding-left: 1.5em; margin-left: 2em;">Commanding officer of Clarkes to receive, escort, go to Kentucky deliver to Bowman, call on Baker to aid in transportn.</li>
	    <li style="margin-left: 2em;">order on Lynch 1000 lead for Chuckamogga expedn.</li>
	  </ul>
<span class="pb center" title="page number in print edition" id="TSJN-01-03-02-pb-0422">[422<a style="padding-left: 0px" onclick="window.open('/img-document-get.xqy?image=TSJN/Pages/TSJN-01-03/TSJN-01-03-02-pb-0422.jpg', 'pageImage', 'scrollbars=1,resizable=1'); return false" onkeypress="this.onclick();" tabindex="0" title="Click to view image of page from print edition"><img src="/img-ML/page-icon.gif" width="18" height="20" style="vertical-align:middle;" alt="page icon"/></a>]</span>
<table class="bodytext">
<tr>
	      <td></td>
	      <td style="text-align: left; text-indent: 0;">detamt. Crockett</td>
	      <td class="brace" rowspan="3"><img src="images/brace-close-trans.png" alt="}" class="brace" style="height: 3.5em; width: 17px;"/></td>
	      <td rowspan="3" style="vertical-align: middle;">Sandy</td>
	      <td></td>
	    </tr>
<tr>
	      <td>22.<a class="ptr" href="#TSJN-01-03-0490-fn-0001" id="TSJN-01-03-0490-fn-0001-ptr">1</a></td>
	      <td style="text-align: left; text-indent: 0;">Botetourt</td>
	      <td style="text-align: right;">100</td>
	    </tr>
<tr>
	      <td>18.</td>
	      <td style="text-align: left; text-indent: 0;">Rockbridge</td>
	      <td></td>
	    </tr>
<tr>
	      <td>16.</td>
	      <td style="text-align: left; text-indent: 0;">Gr. Brier</td>
	      <td class="brace" rowspan="6"><img src="images/brace-close-trans.png" alt="}" class="brace" style="height: 8em; width: 22px;"/></td>
	      <td rowspan="6" style="vertical-align: middle;">Fort Randolph</td>
	      <td></td>
	    </tr>
<tr>
	      <td>43.</td>
	      <td style="text-align: left; text-indent: 0;">Augusta</td>
	      <td></td>
	    </tr>
<tr>
	      <td>15.</td>
	      <td style="text-align: right;">Rockingham</td>
	      <td></td>
	    </tr>
<tr>
	      <td>30.</td>
	      <td style="text-align: left; text-indent: 0;">Frederick</td>
	      <td style="text-align: right;">150</td>
	    </tr>
